{"tid":1912474,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"申訴專員查CSI口罩去向 梁籌庭：存貨像自己有腳","createTime":"2020-03-06T05:54:45.000Z","updateTime":"2020-03-06T15:58:23.000Z","uid":1086,"like":27,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":29,"replies":[{"pid":"0088d374ed8ffd8ea5c28b3522ec9c7d13f0c04c","tid":1912474,"uid":1086,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-06T05:54:45.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/Sdm..829ffUFJ4N6O7yoGA--~A/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjtzbT0xO3c9NzUwO2g9NjUwO2lsPXBsYW5l/http://media.zenfs.com/en_us/News/singtao/20200306a094829.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fs.yimg.com%2Fny%2Fapi%2Fres%2F1.2%2FSdm..829ffUFJ4N6O7yoGA--~A%2FYXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjtzbT0xO3c9NzUwO2g9NjUwO2lsPXBsYW5l%2Fhttp%3A%2F%2Fmedia.zenfs.com%2Fen_us%2FNews%2Fsingtao%2F20200306a094829.jpg&h=c489bc9f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n【星島日報報道】申訴專員公署昨日宣布展開主動調查，審研有關懲教署生產的口罩（坊間俗稱「CSI口罩」），在生產、分發和點存方面的安排。但有公務員工會認為追查困難，因物流署將CSI口罩分發予70多個政府部門。他又指，疫情下的CSI口罩存貨像<span style=\"color: red;\">「自己有腳」般很快消失</span>。<br />\n<br />\n申訴專員將向懲教署及物流署展開主動調查，審研兩部門在規管CSI口罩的生產、分發和點存方面的機制、程序和執行情況。公務員工會聯合會總幹事梁籌庭認為，作主動調查是好事，但擔心追查困難，且無足夠人手去做<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />。<br />\n<br />\n他早上在電台節目上指出，各部門會按季度向物流署取貨，之後的存放及使用事宜由部門自行負責。在無疫情時，處理CSI口罩的指引寬鬆，但他形容在疫情下，口罩存貨像「自己有腳」般很快消失<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />。<br />\n<br />\n民主黨立法會議員涂謹申則透露，曾向物流署查詢口罩分發到各部門的數量，但無獲回答<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />。"},{"pid":"b5c132734d5245e0915fec320b5949f5d9532fd5","tid":1912474,"uid":51271,"like":31,"dislike":0,"score":31,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-06T05:56:30.000Z","msg":"四隻腳果d咬走晒"},{"pid":"1f1cd0c64d753dd82cf4f87b5767804a22f8dcc3","tid":1912474,"uid":3241,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-06T05:58:35.000Z","msg":"有賊就有賊啦屌你老母"},{"pid":"c6dcf87bfc805cbc8f347d78367753b42374ad35","tid":1912474,"uid":49359,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-06T05: